      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/28/1/429/5",
      "text": [
        " الله عز وجل: \" ومن يقتل مؤمنا متعمدا فجزاؤه جهنم \" قال: جزاؤه جهنم إن جازاه."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.basel-kadem": [
          "5.\tWith this chain of narrators, from Hussain bin Sa’eed, from Hammad bin Isa, from Abu’l-Safatij, from Abu Abdillah, peace be upon him, with regards to the saying of Allah, Exalted and Glorious is He: «And the one who kills a believer intentionally, his reward is Hell» <a href=\"/books/quran:4#h93\">[4:93]</a>. He said: His reward is Hell when He is to reward him."
        ]
      }
